===Verb===
{{en-verb|dimpl|ing}}
# {{transitive}} To create a dimple in.
#: ''The hailstorm '''dimpled''' the roof of our car.'' 
# {{intransitive}} To create a dimple in one's face by [[smiling]].
#:''The young girl '''dimpled''' in glee as she was handed a cupcake.''

